Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:23.04,Caligula,,0,0,0,,鳴子!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:26.05,SONG-11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(54,38)}看吧 鬥爭才是真理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:31.64,SONG-11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(54,38)}你們活躍的舞台 僅是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:28.88,Caligula,,0,0,0,,爆炸吧!
